{"tid":2155193,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"釣魚人士經過中國海域    遭中國海警截查","createTime":"2020-08-13T15:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T15:12:25.000Z","uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b52bd1a54b6278e7477b0d52cd64f8c94b7f12c7","tid":2155193,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T15:01:19.000Z","msg":"【釣魚人士經過中國海域    遭中國海警截查】<br />\n<br />\n    有消息人士指，於今晨時分，有幾名釣魚人士經過中國海域(担杆列島) ，欲住公海釣魚。經過中國海域時，遭中國海警截停搜查，其後送往伶仃島。<br />\n<br />\n    消息指，中國海警為避免病毒傳入中國，所以進行截查，並命令離開。最終全部人士獲放行。<br />\n<br />\n13/08/2020<br />\n<br />\n[In Strive | For Truth] <br />\n[堅持｜ 真相］<br />\n<br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/19hkmedia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F19hkmedia%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBRxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=69c3a4a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/19hkmedia/</a><br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/19hk.media\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F19hk.media&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBRxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=5e66d069\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/19hk.media</a><br />\nTg Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/nineteenMedia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FnineteenMedia&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBRxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=35a94ff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nineteenMedia</a><br />\nYouTube: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCK4dRkKRrlN6PpBSefpxvTQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCK4dRkKRrlN6PpBSefpxvTQ%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBRxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=b2064603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCK4dRkKRrlN6PpBSefpxvTQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n#拾玖傳媒<br />\n#nineteenmedia<br />\n#19media<br />\n#歡迎讀者報料<br />\n#歡迎讀者投稿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hxUCf90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-sr